Class LockObj

  • java.lang.Object
    • LockObj

  • public class LockObj
extends java.lang.Object

    Lock Object

    The LockObj stores information about a lock held by a Transaction. These locks are used to determine if a Transaction can access a variable a particular Site.
    Author:
    scottfloam and pratikkarnik
